text: Wielen is a small village in the County of Bentheim in Lower Saxony, Germany, and belongs to the Joint Community (Samtgemeinde) of Uelsen. ==Constituent communities== Along with the namesake Ortsteil, there are outlying centres named Balderhaar, Striepe and Vennebrügge. ==References== ==Other websites== *Wielen *Joint Community’s webpage Category:County of Bentheim (district)
title: Wielen
